text: Grove Street may refer to: *Grove Street (Camden County, New Jersey) *Grove Street (Hudson County, New Jersey) *Grove Street Cemetery *Grove Street Elementary School *"Grove St. Party", a 2011 song by Waka Flocka Flame *Magpie Lane, Oxford, a lane in England's historic university town of Oxford; known as "Grove Street" from the late 19th century until the late 1920s *A historic street in New York City's West Village, part of the larger Greenwich Village *A street in the 2004 video game Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas and the 2013 video game Grand Theft Auto V with the Grove Street Families gang in the aforementioned video games named for it ==See also== *Grove Street station (disambiguation)
title: Grove Street
